snippet.title: RUSHAWAY - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
RUSHAWAY Is Now Finally available to purchase:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2091540/RUSHAWAY/

A 2.5D fast-paced single-player platformer, where your objective is to find the fastest ways towards the goal. Explore different paths for every level, and discover the more optimal ones, avoiding or exploiting different hazards.

Follow us on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Ninestudiosgame 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ninestudiosgames.rushaway
